OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCarer shortage prompts     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcalls to 'boost' fostering 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have been urged to "rocket   
OL,6, boost" fostering to tackle a shortage  
OL,7, of carers.                             
OL,9,FDame Rachel de Souza, the Children's   
OL,10,FCommissioner for England, has warned   
OL,11,Fthat 71% of people who complete a      
OL,12,Ffostering form subsequently drop out.  
OL,14,FShe fears bureaucracy may be putting   
OL,15,Fpeople off and has suggested ministers 
OL,16,Fcould learn from the success of the    
OL,17,FHomes from Ukraine scheme.             
OL,19,FThe government has said it is investing
OL,20,F#27m in the foster care system.        
